
==== Droudsound Beta 3 ====


= QUICKSTART =

Put your music in a directory called "MODS" on your sdcard.

Zip-files and directories will be scanned and indexed.




= NOTES = 

You can search for songs by title.

Long press Back/Forward to skip subsongs and jump directly to next file.

Long press Back to go to top directory

Name songs "<author> - <title>.ext" and it that metadata will be used
if none is found in the file.




= FORMATS =

All formats handled by libsidplay2, modlug and GME, the most popular;

SID, MOD, XM, IT, S3M, NFS, GBS, SPC, AY



-- Sasq
